{"tid":1823851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來林鄭一早教咗我地點應對五毛攻勢","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T23:16:03.000Z","uid":283912,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"814afb1ea433dd3c82757e8c2a6edab1f88cc9b3","tid":1823851,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"踏入2020樂易玲上場後,對家明顯有新佈局<br />\n連登內外五毛行動引起多次大型分化活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元旦捉鬼事件<br />\n勇武小隊退場事件<br />\n黃色經濟圈內部偽黃批鬥<br />\n和你影爭論<br />\n大量眨和捧勇言論<br />\n九月勸交四眼仔被bin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對對家大規模拋出唔同議題分化引起我地內部分裂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要緊守一個原則做共識就可以化解</span><br />\n就係林奠媽媽嘅:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>we connect</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天琦講過政治就係要歸納更多本黎唔支持自己嘅人<br />\n但留意下以上五毛叫你做嘅行動有咩共通點?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係想我地走極端自我孤立</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地好叻用我哋嘅語言偷換概念,例如<br />\n-又話核爆都唔割依家xxx就割<br />\n-又話各有各做,依家xxx就阻人做<br />\n-原來連登仔都支持放過xxx<br />\n-xxx打手睇黎好驚<br />\n仲有大絕,用被打被濫捕被自殺手足道德綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得點解要有民間記者會?<br />\n點解要有連儂牆?點解要整死cctvb?<br />\n點解要打twitter/國際戰線?.....<br />\n就係因為我哋要connect最多盟友/民意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人民團結係極端最怕嘅事</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而人多先可以將各樣行動威力推到最大<br />\n無論係遊行,選舉,黃色經濟圈...<br />\n什至係勇武行動嘅時候和理非作為盾嘅功能<br />\n(19才子都講過支那最不解係點解我地識將和勇一陰一陽咁交替上場合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n記住,我地唔係惡霸係與民為善嘅抗爭者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敵人只有一個:支那及其爪牙(港共+黑警)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對藍絲(有理智),偽黃,其他立場模糊嘅人<br />\n盡量感化拉攏,感化唔到都唔好將佢推去對立面<br />\n不分化不割蓆同時應該加多樣:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不無謂樹敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n而關於互相屈毛問題,只要調返轉黎諗<br />\n如果你潛入藍屍gp你會叫佢地冷靜行事<br />\n定帶風向令佢地魯莽行動出錯樹敵?<br />\n再套返落連登就知五毛係吹和風定極端風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要頭腦清醒,目標對準,五毛就無所遁形<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇氣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>智慧</strong></span></span></span>也永不滅阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49ec6fd69b6ec672a85ad6a137ab428b9230bd8","tid":1823851,"uid":266010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"點都好,林鄭唔喺手足啊！"},{"pid":"9995732314dbc778dde6cf17a723f0dd173affad","tid":1823851,"uid":29381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"忍手咪覆d分化post咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c7b59c77a2174aa879130eaa7a7e75e89fef97","tid":1823851,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9995732314dbc778dde6cf17a723f0dd173affad","tid":1823851,"uid":29381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"忍手咪覆d分化post咪得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"五毛會自己圍爐推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecca696030684f0323432e476d71e218a7efd3e6","tid":1823851,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a49ec6fd69b6ec672a85ad6a137ab428b9230bd8","tid":1823851,"uid":266010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:1